{"tid":1045943,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【大時代】傳中美或月底落實全面貿易協議","createTime":"2019-03-04T01:08:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-04T05:10:32.000Z","uid":66271,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"00120202850a037f2b530cb30afc0b4c897f8ffa","tid":1045943,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T01:08:11.000Z","msg":"《華爾街日報》報道，中美就達成最終貿易協議達最後階段，中方提出降低美國農產品、化學、汽車及其他產品關稅，美方考慮撤銷全部或大部分去年對華貨品實施的關稅。消息指雙方面對各自本土壓力，認為各自的讓步太多，但中美談判取得進展，並可在中美元首於3月27日峰會達成協議，中國國家主席習近平屆時完成意大利及法國的訪問。<br />\n<br />\n中方在協議中承諾公平競爭環境，包括加快取消外資在汽車業持股佔比限制，與及進一步減少目前15%進口汽車關稅。中方同時增加從美國購買產品，包括180億美元天然氣。雙方亦繼續商討中國工業政策，美方不滿目前政策過於優待中國國企。(fc/w)"},{"pid":"84527b70623ceb5044e9f4ad2a38eb8263b22db4","tid":1045943,"uid":196625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T01:11:00.000Z","msg":"得啦又贏啦"},{"pid":"c61b098dd6af6f698c7767968ec470201bb39944","tid":1045943,"uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T01:15:36.000Z","msg":"我諗就有排都唔會攪得掂"},{"pid":"057e2affa8d888e67f3ef26239865fd249c213be","tid":1045943,"uid":198008,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T01:28:12.000Z","msg":"又傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60ba30bfd6214ce0a9bd37caaaca7c9ef650de92","tid":1045943,"uid":224533,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T02:24:36.000Z","msg":"lm等睇再延期"},{"pid":"32e686e9f0ff1a5d9db4cb0b6a9f49b9ce1971c7","tid":1045943,"uid":199669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T02:25:16.000Z","msg":"日日都傳"},{"pid":"44b0fcca91b98ceaac69066d6a6ade9afec0dd53","tid":1045943,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"32e686e9f0ff1a5d9db4cb0b6a9f49b9ce1971c7","tid":1045943,"uid":199669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T02:25:16.000Z","msg":"日日都傳"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T04:08:05.000Z","msg":"升